📘 Resources & Cheat Sheets

Resource Use Case Link
MITRE ATT&CK (https://attack.mitre.org/) Tactics, techniques, and procedures (TTPs) 🔗 Visit (https://attack.mitre.org/)
CyberChef (https://gchq.github.io/CyberChef/) Encode, decode, parse, and analyze data 🔗 Visit (https://gchq.github.io/CyberChef/)
Red Team Tools (https://github.com/yeyintminthuhtut/Awesome-Red-Teaming) Offensive security tools list 🔗 Visit (https://github.com/yeyintminthuhtut/Awesome-Red-Teaming)
Blue Team Tools (https://github.com/meitar/awesome-blue-team) Defensive tools for analysts 🔗 Visit (https://github.com/meitar/awesome-blue-team)


